Text: This happens to me too. I never plan for it and I always end up bloated and feeling like I look fat.

Text: I’m one of those people who can’t poop outside of their house, I went on a 5 days trip and OOOOH BOY came back with 2 extra KGs, you best believe I was fat, a whale, a pig.
